Any award made pursuant to this chapter shall be reduced by the amount of any payments received or to be received by the claimant as a result of the injury from the following sources:
From or on behalf of the person who committed the crime;
Under insurance programs mandated by law;
From public funds;
Under any contract of insurance wherein the claimant is the insured or beneficiary;
As an emergency award pursuant to KRS 346.120; and
From donations made on behalf of the victim or claimant toward expenses incurred as a result of the crime.
